snippet.title: Project P
snippet.description: In my channel I will be discussing various things including things that happening at the moment, giving my thoughts to all kinds of videos, pictures, and memes as well. I'll also sometimes do public reactions, social experiments, and public interviews. They're going to have a lot of entertaining and funny videos so stick around. Make sure you subscribe and stay tuned for the next videos because I am going to be uploading daily every week.
